LWP-Authen-OAuth version 1.01
=============================

This module provides a sub-class of LWP::UserAgent that generates OAuth 1.0
signed requests. You should familiarise yourself with OAuth at
http://oauth.net/.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  LWP::UserAgent
  Digest::SHA
  MIME::Base64
  URI
  URI::Escape

